Boil spaghetti in salted water until al dente. While the spaghetti is cooking, saute the onions until golden. Add pepperoni and black olives and saute, stirring, 1 minute. To the pepperoni mixture add cooked and drained spaghetti, Savory Market Pepperoni Pizza Flavor, parsley, and cook over low heat, tossing, 1 minute. Remove skillet from heat and stir in Parmesan and salt and pepper to taste.